  <brief_title>Applications Site Reactions After Injection of Insulin Detemir and Saline in Subjects With Diabetes</brief_title>
  <acronym>APPLY</acronym>
  <official_title>Doubleblind, Randomised, Single Centre Investigator Sponsored Study of Applications Site Reactions After Deep and Superficial Subcutaneous and Intradermal Injection of Insulin Detemir and Saline in Subjects With Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
