  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare application site reactions after superficial and deep subcutaneous and intradermal
      injections of insulin detemir and saline in patients with diabetes

      - The patient serves as his own control, n=100 patients with diabetes
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
